-- Paul Reynolds Appointed Chairman at Canaccord U.K., Vlaad Says
-- B y   K a t i a   D m i t r i e v a
-- 2013-07-12T18:02:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-12/paul-reynolds-appointed-chairman-at-canaccord-u-k-vlaad-says.html
Canaccord Financial Inc. appointed
Chief Executive Officer Paul Reynolds chairman of its U.K. unit,
replacing Tim Hoare, according to Vlaad & Co., a Toronto-based
financial-services recruiting firm.  Other moves noted in the “Bill’s Buzz” weekly  newsletter 
include:  *  National Bank of Canada (NA)  hired  Alex Smith  as a managing
director of its diversified investment banking team from Morgan
Stanley in the U.K.  * In New York, RBC Capital Markets added William Argiriou and J.
Chris McCormack as co-heads of the energy futures desk. Both
join from UBS where Argiriou was head of New York commodities
and McCormack was executive director, exchange traded
derivatives.  * Bastion Infrastructure Group added Lindsay Caldwell as a
senior associate, investments from Borealis Infrastructure.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katia Dmitrieva in Toronto at 
